# Git commits and Conventional Commits

Whenever you prepare, draft, review, or run a `git commit` (including amend or message-only changes), read and follow the project skill at `.cursor/skills/conventional-commits/SKILL.md`.

Do not write commit subjects or bodies that conflict with that skill unless the user explicitly overrides it in the same conversation.
